---
title: Carb Smart Jalapeño-Chorizo Chili with Cheddar Cheese
description: This nourishing, low-carb chili swaps out traditional beans for lots of wholesome veggies! Spicy jalapeños and melty cheddar cheese amp up the deliciousness.

Carb Smart (50 g carbohydrates or less) is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.

